`CreatesShroud` inherits from `RevealsShroud`, but every actor with `CreatesShroud` also has  `RevealsShroud` in the MiniYaml (`GAP` in `mods/ra/rules/structures.yaml:78-83`, `MGG` in `mods/ra/rules/vehicles.yaml:504-507`).

Separating the two would be the most flexible option.

`CreatesShroud` _currently_ derives from `RevealsShroud`:

``` c#
    public class CreatesShroud : RevealsShroud
    {
        public CreatesShroud(Actor self, CreatesShroudInfo info)
            : base(self, info)
        {
```

I'm proposing that that be change to:

``` c#
    public class CreatesShroud : AffectsShroud
    {
        public CreatesShroud(Actor self, CreatesShroudInfo info)
            : base(self, info)
        {
```

where `AffectsShroud` is an absract base class for `RevealsShroud` & `CreatesShroud`.
